Entry.JapaneseText: ダオス……本当にあなたは 変わってしまったんだね……
Entry.EnglishText: Dhaos...So it really is true. You truly have changed...

Entry.JapaneseText: おまえは、私のことなど 何も知っていない
私にあるのは後悔と復讐、 それのみだ
Entry.EnglishText: The only thing left inside me is regret and apprehension.

Entry.JapaneseText: 後悔……復讐…… 何のための……
……ここにいたダオスは 別の時空から飛んできた ダオスだったのか……？
Entry.EnglishText: ...That Dhaos just now...Could he have travelled from a different time here?

Entry.JapaneseText: ごめん…… みんなにはいろいろ、 迷惑かけちゃったね
Entry.EnglishText: I'm so sorry...I've put everyone in trouble for my own selfish reasons all along...

Entry.JapaneseText: 私は幼い時、ダオスと、 世界樹の前で出会った
Entry.EnglishText: I met Dhaos when I was really small, in front of the Mana Tree.

Entry.JapaneseText: デリス・カーラーン…… 自分の故郷に『大いなる実り』を 持ち帰るためにそこへ来てた
Entry.EnglishText: He told me of Derris Kharlan...How he needed a Mana Seed and return to his home planet...

Entry.JapaneseText: あの頃、優しくて、 思慮深いヤツだったよ、 あいつは
Entry.EnglishText: At that time he was so very kind to me. He used to be a very thoughtful and gentle man.

Entry.JapaneseText: そう。だから、そんな彼が、 人類に戦争を仕掛けた張本人 だなんてとても思えなかった
Entry.EnglishText: Yes, the same. That's why when I heard he was spearheading a war against humanity I couldn't bring myself to believe it.

Entry.JapaneseText: だから、確かめたかった。 ダオスがあのダオスなのか
Entry.EnglishText: That's the reason I had to be sure if that Dhaos was my Dhaos.

Entry.JapaneseText: そうだとしたら、 止めなきゃって……
Entry.EnglishText: And if that was the case...I promised myself to stop him with my own two hands.

Entry.JapaneseText: でも、怖くて聞けなかった…… 何も、ちゃんと……
Entry.EnglishText: But I never imagined it would be so scary. It was all true...All they said...
Guess I never was cut for the job, huh?

Entry.JapaneseText: そっか…… <RND_P>さん、 ダオスのこと……
ん……あれ…… 何があった、の……？
これは……！ 魔科学兵器のかけらだ……！
Entry.EnglishText: I can't believe it...! It's the fragment of a Magitech weapon!

Entry.JapaneseText: <Red>ヴァルハラ<White>で『シグルド』が 使ってたものじゃないかな
Entry.EnglishText: These seem to be leftovers from Sigurd's attack on Valhalla.

Entry.JapaneseText: 爆発すると自動的に 詠唱を続けて、 魔法を継続させる兵器だよ
Entry.EnglishText: It's a weapon that destroys the nearby landscape by continuously casting spells automatically, quickly depleting the surrounding Mana.
That's it! This is the source of the Prism Ring!

Entry.JapaneseText: わたしが魔術を使ったはずみに 爆発して……？
Entry.EnglishText: You mean it wasn't the explosion caused by my magic...?

Entry.JapaneseText: なんだ……<MEL>の せいじゃねーよな、 これって
Entry.EnglishText: This means...It never was <MEL>'s fault to begin with!

Entry.JapaneseText: せいじゃないってことはないよ。 爆発させた原因はわたしだもん
Entry.EnglishText: I may not have caused it, but the explosion definitely set the machine off.

Entry.JapaneseText: わたし、魔術使うたび怖かった。 また暴走させちゃうんじゃ ないかって
Entry.EnglishText: All this time... I've been so very scared of my magic causing a disaster again...

Entry.JapaneseText: うん……よかったよ、 本当に……
……ま、これで 一件落着ってことかな
Entry.EnglishText: Well! That means everything is settled now, right?

Entry.JapaneseText: ふたりのことも見届けられたし、 自分たちの時代に戻ろうか
Entry.EnglishText: Since we've made sure you guys could finish your job, it's about time we returned to our own eras.

Entry.JapaneseText: 指輪も いい感じになってるし
Entry.EnglishText: Looks like my ring is ready to rock, too!

Entry.JapaneseText: 私がみんなを元の時代に 送ったげるよ
Entry.EnglishText: How about I send you back to your own times?

Entry.JapaneseText: <RND_P>はどうすんだ。 またダオスを……
Entry.EnglishText: So what now, Rody? I mean Dhaos...

Entry.JapaneseText: できればそうしたいけど、 どこ行ったかわかんないし
Entry.EnglishText: I could try to track him down but I don't have the slightest idea where he went.

Entry.JapaneseText: この指輪の気まぐれに 付き合ってみてもいいかなって。 風の向くままにさ
Entry.EnglishText: I've grown a bit tired of the whim of this ring, to be honest. So I might try to track him down with normal means.

Entry.JapaneseText: あっ……来た…… ほら、みんな
それじゃあ、 <DIO>、<MEL>、がんばって
Entry.EnglishText: In that case...<DIO>, <MEL>, always do your best!

Entry.JapaneseText: <ARC>、元気でな。 寂しくて、泣くなよ
Entry.EnglishText: It's been nice <ARC>... If you get sad...don't cry, kay?

Entry.JapaneseText: 泣くかっ！ このスカポンタン！ 空気読め！
Entry.EnglishText: I won't cry you braggart jerk! Way to ruin the mood.

Entry.JapaneseText: おふたりに会えて、 友達ができたみたいで 楽しかったです
Entry.EnglishText: I am glad we met. It has been a really fun experience.

Entry.JapaneseText: ありがとうございます
Entry.EnglishText: Thank you from the bottom of my heart.

Entry.JapaneseText: 友達だもんね、 わたしたち
……ってまだ 終わってねーだろ
だってノルンに言われた 『なりきり士』の仕事 オレら、なんもしてねーぞ？
Entry.EnglishText: Have you forgotten? We've got a job as Roleplayer!

Entry.JapaneseText: あ……そうだっけ…… そうだね
自分たちで事件起こして 自分たちで解決しただけだもんね
Entry.EnglishText: I think after all you've been through that was easy to forget.

Entry.JapaneseText: どーせ、またどこ行くか、 わかってないんでしょ
Entry.EnglishText: Where to? You have no idea, do you?

Entry.JapaneseText: でも…… わかんねーから おもしれーんじゃん！
Entry.EnglishText: But...not knowing is the most fun, isn't it?

Entry.JapaneseText: あー待ってよ！ 置いてかないで〜！！
Entry.EnglishText: H-hey wait! Don't leave me here!
